  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/blog/announcing-shortlists-2016-atlantic-writing-competition.html">Announcing the Shortlists for the 2016 Atlantic Writing Competition</a></span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content">Thursday, April 14, 2016 - 12:05pm</span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>The Writers' Federation of Nova Scotia is pleased to announce the shortlists for this year's <a href="http://writers.ns.ca/competitions/atlantic-writing-competition-unpublished-manuscripts.html">Atlantic Writing Competition for Unpublished Manuscripts</a>. <strong>The winners will be announced the week of April 18th, 2016.</strong></p>
<p><strong>HR (BILL) PERCY ADULT NOVEL PRIZE<br /></strong>Anne Bishop<em>, Blessed are the Poor <br /></em>Liz Graham, <em>Lord of Misrule</em> <br />Andrea Doukas, <em>Before the Monsoon</em> </p></div>  </div>  
  



  
